hopobject.body: How much notice do you have to give? executivepharmacy.net The next part of the story is obscure, and probably only makes sense to Django Bates. “I overheard my friend the trumpeter Nils Petter Molvaer asking someone how they were. He used this colloquial Norwegian phrase which means ‘Is there anyone you can touch?’ And this got me thinking about touch in music, all the different kinds of touch my trio and the band bring to musical notes. And this gave me a clue as to how I could spin that little melody into a piece.”
